<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="37" type="type material">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="37">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="37">
Lectotype, here designated, female (IRSNB), glued on pinned card, head and pronotum missing, genitalia attached in microvial, labeled: green paper handwritten &quot;rugosa. Pz. Sta Cath.(Dhr.)&quot;/ printed &quot;Soc. Ent. Belg. Coll. Putzeys&quot;/ 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Syntype”">&quot;Syntype&quot;</normalizedToken>
/ &quot;Lectotype Ardistomis rugosa Putz. des. S. W. Nichols 1984&quot;.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="37">
<bibRefCitation author="Putzeys, JAAH" journalOrPublisher="Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique" pageId="34" pageNumber="53" pagination="3 - 242" refId="B32" refString="Putzeys, JAAH, 1866. Revision generale des clivinides. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 10: 3 - 242" title="Revision generale des clivinides." volume="10" year="1866">Putzeys (1866</bibRefCitation>
