</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="38" type="measurements and variation">
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="38">
<pageBreakToken pageId="19" pageNumber="38" start="start">Measurements</pageBreakToken>
and variation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="38">
Variation of measurements (mm) and ratios for 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Putzeys" baseAuthorityYear="1866" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Semiardistomis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rugosus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">Semiardistomis rugosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(n=2) are: HL = 0,71; PL = 1,35; PW = 1,51; EL = 3,72-3,73-3,75; EW = 2,34-2,42-2,50; 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">SBL =</emphasis>
5,78; PW/EW = 0,64; PW/PL = 1,12; PL/EL = 0,36; EW/EL = 0,63.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
